headline: CHEEZ-IT® AND WENDY'S® STACK UP THE FLAVOR WITH LIMITED-EDITION BACONATOR® CRACKERS
summary: When a snack craving hits, only an explosion of flavors can truly satisfy. That's why this summer, Cheez-It® is teaming up with the fast-food innovators at Wendy's® to serve up the ultimate craveable fix: the first-ever Cheez-It x Wendy's Baconator® crackers. This limited-edition collaboration brings together the best of both worlds: mouthwatering Baconator flavor and the signature Cheez-It crunch. It's your go-to snack and your drive-thru must-have combined into an absurdly delicious bite.
